_sText:
This map has taken way too long being in progress, this is because I procrastinated and had months where I didn't even open up hammer :(.

Features of the map:
- 9 shit-stained crappy mpbhop levels that you can prespeed grind your ass on.
- 88.4% brushsides (thanks to propper for that) that you can look at the shitty architecture on each stage with.
- A few jumps that require >400 vel.
- Very possible on legit.
- Auto rand friendly levels (mostly).
- Soundscapes for people to hate on.
- Compiled with HDR so your eyes can bleed out with the brightness.

Things I wish I'd done with the map:
- Bonus (couldn't fit).
- Better start/end room (couldn't fit).
- Better mapping.
- Less lazy mpbhops.
- Not hit about 4 limits in one.

Have fun and remember to RTV before those nerds in the server see the osu level.

(Hopefully I didn't fuck up the packing =D)

Changes in v2:
- Fixes for 4th/5th level skips.
- HDR less eyebleedingly bright (hopefully).
- The singular missing texture is now packed
